%20investigation%20into%20Kareem's%20horrific%20injuries%20showed%20that%20he%20had%20experienced%20cardiac%20arrest%2C%20which%20resulted%20in%20brain%20damage%2C%20a%20shattered%20rib%2C%20a%20lacerated%20liver%2C%20bleeding%20eye%20tissue%2C%20and%20brain%20swelling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDoctors%20at%20a%20hospital%20in%20Cincinnati%20said%20that%20injuries%20on%20the%20one-year-old%20%26quot%3Bcould%20only%20have%20occurred%20from%20violent%20impacts%20against%20objects%20or%20from%20delivered%20blows.%26quot%3B%20Kareem's%20death%20was%20ruled%20a%20homicide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20stated%20that%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20death%2C%20Kareem's%20mother%2C%20Aminata%20Keita%2C%20had%20been%20dating%20Murray%20for%20around%20three%20months.%20The%20complaint%20claims%20that%20on%20May%201%2C%20Murray%20took%20Kareem%20inside%20and%20put%20him%20%26quot%3Bdirectly%20to%20bed%26quot%3B%20after%20they%20had%20been%20playing%20outside%20the%20house.%20The%2023-year-old%20added%20that%20the%20boy%20skipped%20meals%20since%20he%20was%20tired.%20According%20to%20the%20authorities%2C%20Murray%20claimed%20to%20have%20spent%20%26quot%3Bseveral%20minutes%26quot%3B%20in%20Kareem's%20bedroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prosecutors%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BMurray%20was%20unable%20to%20provide%20any%20alternate%20explanation%20for%20how%20K.K.%20could%20have%20been%20injured%20so%20severely.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20online%20court%20documents%20seen%20by%20the%20outlet%2C%20Murray%20has%20been%20charged%20with%20two%20charges%20of%20murder%2C%20one%20crime%20of%20assault%2C%20and%20one%20case%20of%20endangering%20the%20welfare%20of%20a%20child.%20%26quot%3BThis%20case%20is%20both%20heartbreaking%20and%20sickening.%20I%20cannot%20imagine%20the%20amount%20of%20evil%20required%20to%20hurt%20an%20innocent%20child%20so%20severely.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20genuinely%20disturbing%20to%20think%20someone%20capable%20of%20doing%20this%20might%20walk%20among