0all%20the%20way%20in%20the%20tournament%2C%20courtesy%20of%20their%20defeat%20against%20RR%20in%20the%20Eliminator%2C%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%20star%20Tushar%20Deshpande%20shared%20an%20Instagram%20story%20mocking%20the%20Bengaluru%20side.%20But%20later%2C%20deleted%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20to%20Instagram%2C%20the%20CSK%20pacer%20Deshpande%20shared%20a%20story%20that%20read%3A%20%26quot%3BCSK%20fans%20are%20built%20different%26quot%3B%20with%20a%20picture%20of%20'Bengaluru%20Cant'%20railway%20station.%20Understanding%20the%20backlash%20over%20such%20a%20post%2C%20Deshpande%20then%20deleted%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ETushar%20Deshpande's%20Instagram%20story.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FbXSed8pf7Y%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FbXSed8pf7Y%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Mufaddal%20Vohra%20(%40mufaddal_vohra)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmufaddal_vohra%2Fstatus%2F1793344387679670767%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMay%2022%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20match%2C%20chasing%20173%2C%20Rajasthan%20ended%20with%20174%2F6%20as%20Rovman%20Powell%20(16%20not%20out)%20provided%20the%20finishing%20touches%20in%20a%20tense%20finish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20he%20has%20done%20several%20times%20before%20this%20season%2C%20Riyan%20Parag%20(36%20off%2026)%20showcased%20deep%20resolve%20in%20an%20adverse%20situation%20to%20help%20Rajasthan%20stay%20alive%20in%20the%20tournament.%20It%20was%20Royals'%20first%20win%20after%20four%20losses%20and%20an%20abandoned%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2008%20winners%20Royals%20face%20Sunrisers%20Hyderabad%20in%20Chennai%20on%20Friday%20for%20a%20place%20in%20the%20IPL%20final.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20returning%20Shimron%20Hetmyer%20also%20played%20his%20part%20to%20perfection%2C%20scoring%20a%20crucial%2026%20off%2014%20balls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20contest%20wherein%20fortunes%20swung%20from%20one%20side%20to%20another%2C%20RR%20remained%20ahead%20with%20impactful%20performances%20throughout%20even%20though%20Mohammed%20Siraj%20(2%2F33)%20raised%20late%20hopes%20for%20RCB%20with%20wickets%20of%20Parag%20and%20Hetmyer%20in%20the%2018th%20over%2C%20With%2013%20needed%20off%20last%20two%20overs%2C%20Powell%20found%20two%20fours%20off%20Lockie%20Ferguson%20to%20seal%20the%20deal%20in%20favour%20of%20his%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20it%20was%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%20(45%20off%2030)%20who%20gave%20them%20the%20impetus%20at%20the%20top.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOff%20to%20an%20unconvincing%20start%20with%20his%20initial%20runs%20coming%20off%20the%20outside%20edge%2C%20Jaiswal%20grew%20in%20confidence%20when%20Yash%20Dayal%20fed%20him%20a%20few%20deliveries%20to%20capitalise%20on%20and%20the%20RR%20opener%20cracked%20four%20fours%20in%20the%20third%20over%20to%20break%20the%20shackles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20other%20end%2C%20Tom%20Kohler-Cadmore%20(20)%20also%20hit%20a%20couple%20of%20fours%20against%20Siraj%20and%20while%20getting%20a%20lifeline%20from%20Glenn%20Maxwell%2C%20who%20spilled%20a%20sitter%20at%20deep%20square%20leg%20off%20Dayal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20RR's%20acceleration%20rapidly%20shaving%20runs%20off%20the%20target%2C%20RCB%20needed%20a%20breakthrough%20and%20Lockie%20Ferguson%20provided%20the%20first%20success%20when%20he%20foxed%20Kohler-Cadmore%20with%20a%20slow%20yorker%20which%20crashed%20into%20the%20stumps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20gradual%20progression%20of%20Jaiswal's%20innings%20saw%20the%20batter%20finding%20his%20rhythm%2C%20but%20the%20extreme%20heat%20sapped%20him%20out%20completely%20having%20faced%20a%20mere%2029%20balls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20between%20the%20ninth%20and%20the%2010th%20over%2C%20Jaiswal%20received%20on-field%20treatment%20and%20got%20back%20up%20only%20to%20play%20a%20loose%20shot%20%E2%80%94%20an%20attempted%20ramp%20off%20Cameron%20Green%20but%20only%20gloved%20it%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98keeper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%2C%20Karn%20Sharma%20dealt%20a%20body%20blow%20by%20having%20Sanju%20Samson%20(17)%20stumped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20their%20tails%20up%2C%20RCB%20continued%20making%20inroads%20with%20Dhruv%20Jurel%20(8)%20being%20run%20out%20after%20a%20brilliant%20effort%20from%20Virat%20Kohli%20and%20Cameron%20Green.%20Kohli%20fired%20a%20sharp%20throw%20from%20deep%20midwicket%20to%20the%20non-striker's%20end%2C%20where%20Jurel%20was%20found%20short%20of%20his%20crease.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERR%20were%20firmly%20under%20pressure%20heading%20into%20the%2015th%20over%20when%20they%20chose%20to%20go%20after%20Green%2C%20who%20had%20been%20all%20over%20them%20with%20three%20tidy%20overs%20and%20a%20wicket%20up%20until%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHetmyer%20smacked%20the%20Australian%20for%20a%20six%20and%20Parag%20followed%20his%20partner%20in%20hitting%20another%2C%20while%20also%20finding%20a%20four%20to%20collect%2017%20runs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20PTI%20inputs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716431160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F5uur1e0o_virat-kohli-rcb-bcci_625x300_23_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fcsk-star-rubs-salt-on-rcbs-wounds-with-instagram-story-deletes-it-after-backlash-5723691%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chennai%20Super%20Kings%20star%20mocked%20RCB%20over%20their%20repeated%20failure%20to%20lift%20the%20IPL%20title%20on%20social%20media%2C%20but%20later%20deleted%20the%20story%20he%20had%20posted%20on%20Instagram.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fcsk-star-rubs-salt-on-rcbs-wounds-with-instagram-story-deletes-it-after-backlash-5723691%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fcsk-star-rubs-salt-on-rcbs-w