20being%20bound%20and%20bundled%20into%20a%20jeep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20friends%20in%20Palestine%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20of%20the%20conscripts%2C%2019-year-old%20Naama%20Levy%2C%20pleads%20in%20English.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20gunmen%20can%20be%20heard%20shouting%20back%20in%20Arabic%3A%20%26quot%3BYou%20are%20dogs!%20We%20will%20step%20on%20you%2C%20dogs!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hostages%20Families%20Forum%2C%20which%20represents%20relatives%20of%20the%20124%20people%20-%20mostly%20civilians%20-%20still%20held%20by%20Hamas%2C%20said%20the%20footage%20was%20recovered%20from%20bodycams%20worn%20by%20gunmen%20who%20attacked%20the%20Nahal%20Oz%20base%20in%20southern%20Israel%20where%20the%20women%20served%20as%20surveillance%20spotters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShots%20of%20killed%20Israeli%20soldiers%20were%20excluded%20and%20publication%20was%20approved%20by%20the%20families%20of%20the%20five%20captives%2C%20the%20forum%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Israeli%20government%20must%20not%20waste%20another%20moment%3B%20it%20must%20return%20to%20the%20negotiating%20table%20today!%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20Forum%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20says%201%2C200%20people%20were%20killed%20and%20more%20than%20250%20abducted%20in%20the%20Oct.%207%20attack%20led%20by%20Hamas.%20Israel%20responded%20by%20launching%20an%20offensive%20to%20eliminate%20the%20Islamist%20group%20in%20which%20Gaza%20health%20authorities%20say%20more%20than%2035%2C000%20Palestinians%20have%20been%20killed.%20Israel's%20military%20says%20286%20Israeli%20soldiers%20have%20also%20been%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENetanyahu's%20government%20says%20continued%20military%20pressure%20will%20force%20Hamas%20to%20yield.%20Hostage%20families%20fear%20their%20loved%20ones%20will%20not%20survive%20and%20that%20the%20women%20captives%20may%20be%20raped.%20Hamas%20has%20denied%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20abuse%20by%20its%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20ple