o%20shareholder%20pressure.%20Just%20this%20month%2C%20he%20announced%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finvestors.buzzfeed.com%2Fnews-releases%2Fnews-release-details%2Fbuzzfeed-inc-bullish-about-future-company-redefines-compensation%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20plan%20that%20ties%20his%20compensation%20to%20the%20company's%20stock%20performance%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20convince%20investors%20that%20he's%20really%20serious%20about%20turning%20things%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20again%3A%20What's%20Ramaswamy's%20actual%20plan%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERamaswamy%20has%20yet%20to%20talk%20to%20BuzzFeed's%20board%20or%20management%2C%20says%20a%20person%20familiar%20with%20the%20company.%20Ramaswamy%20has%20not%20responded%20to%20my%20request%20for%20comment%2C%20so%20we're%20just%20going%20to%20have%20to%20guess%20here.%20A%20few%20theories%20from%20the%20peanut%20gallery%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt's%20the%20money!%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20This%20is%20the%20most%20obvious%20answer%20because%20it's%20why%20any%20activist%20shareholder%20invests%20in%20a%20company.%20They%20may%20say%20they%20have%20better%20strategy%2C%20or%20that%20management%20is%20incompetent%2C%20or%20whatever.%20What%20they%20really%20want%20is%20for%20shares%20in%20the%20company%20to%20be%20worth%20more%20than%20what%20they%20paid%20for%20them%2C%20and%20it%20doesn't%20really%20matter%20how%20they%20get%20there.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt's%20the%20clicks!%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Ramaswamy%20likes%20attention%20%E2%80%94%20he%20spent%20%2430%20million%20of%20his%20own%20money%20getting%20himself%20onto%20the%20national%20stage%20last%20year.%20So%20why%20not%20spend%20a%20few%20million%20more%20and%20buy%20his%20very%20own%20media%20platform%3F%20BuzzFeed%20no%20longer%20commands%20the%20same%20kind%20of%20media%20spotlight%20it%20used%20to%2C%20but%20it's%20still%20pretty%20big%20and%20includes%20not%20just%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FBuzzFeed.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBuzzFeed.com%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20also%20The%20Huffington%20Post%20as%20well%20as%20First%20We%20Feast%20%E2%80%94%20better%20known%20as%20the%20company%20that%20makes%20the%20%26quot%3BHot%20Ones%26quot%3B%20viral%20chicken%20wing%2Fcelebrity%20interview%20show.%20(%26quot%3BViral%20chicken%20wing%2Fcelebrity%20interview%20show%26quot%3B%20is%20also%20fun%20to%20type.)%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt's%20a%20troll!%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%244%20million%20is%20a%20lot%20for%20a%20practical%20joke%2C%20but%20Ramaswamy%20(apparently)%20has%20cash%20to%20burn.%20Maybe%20he's%20getting%20a%20kick%20out%20of%20the%20idea%20that%20a%20Trump-loving%20Republican%20can%20cause%20chaos%20at%20a%20media%20company%20famous%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.buzzfeednews.com%2Farticle%2Fkenbensinger%2Fthese-reports-allege-trump-has-deep-ties-to-russia%23.fiq8pA6W%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epublishing%20the%20infamous%20Trump%20%26quot%3Bdossier%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt's%20the%20wings!%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Again%3A%20BuzzFeed%20owns%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DFALlhXl6CmA%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHot%20Ones%2C%20the%20show%20that%20most%20recently%20helped%20Conan%20O'Brien%20take%20over%20the%20internet%20again%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20again%3A%20Ramaswamy%20likes%20attention.%20There%20are%20probably%20cheaper%20ways%20to%20secure%20a%20booking%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FSean_Evans_(interviewer)%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESean%20Evans%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20this%20could%20speed%20things%20up.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EUpdate%3A%20May%2022%2C%202024%20%E2%80%94%20This%20story%20has%20been%20updated%20with%20a%20statement%20from%20a%20BuzzFeed%20spokesperson.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2