eron%20International%20Science%20and%20Engineering%20Fair%20(ISEF)%20attracts%20some%20of%20the%20best%20and%20brightest%20students%20from%20around%20the%20world%2C%20like%20Hawaii%20and%20California%20as%20well%20as%20Kildare%2C%20Ireland%20and%20Shanghai%2C%20China.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPast%20winners%20include%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmanhattan-project-scientists-who-won-nobel-prizes-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ENobel%20Prize%20recipients%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Rhodes%20Scholars%2C%20and%20MacArthur%20Foundation%20genius%20grant%20awardees.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20that%20kind%20of%20money%20and%20acclaim%20on%20the%20line%2C%20it's%20not%20surprising%20that%20the%20atmosphere%20surrounding%20the%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fceo-resignations-stress-pressure-loneliness-work-life-balance-elon-musk-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecompetition%20is%20intense%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20a%20lot%20of%20kids%20who%20are%20here%20actually%20%E2%80%94%20I%20don't%20think%20I'm%20reading%20it%20wrong%20%E2%80%94%20are%20truly%20excited%20to%20be%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Maya%20Ajmera%2C%20the%20president%20and%20CEO%20of%20the%20Society%20for%20Science%2C%20which%20coordinates%20ISEF.%20%26quot%3BBut%20they%20also%20feel%20the%20pressure%20of%20wanting%20to%20win%20and%20the%20pressure%20of%20going%20to%20college%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20Business%20Insider%20last%20week.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparenthood-mistakes-2018-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ebiggest%20mistake%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20parents%20with%20ambitious%2C%20curious%20kids%20can%20make%20is%20adding%20to%20that%20