In%20episode%202%20of%20season%203%2C%20the%20ton%20gathers%20for%20the%20Full%20Moon%20Ball.%20The%20outside%20shots%20were%20filmed%20at%20Osterly%20Park%20and%20House%20in%20west%20London.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20entrance%20of%20Osterly%20Park%20and%20House%20in%20%26quot%3BBridgerton%26quot%3B%20(left)%20and%20an%20angled%20shot%20of%20the%20same%20residence%20from%20the%20side%20showcasing%20its%20front%20gardens%20(right).%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664e45a89fc063e829b3e325%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOsterly%20Park%20and%20House%20in%20%26quot%3BBridgerton%20(left)%20and%20in%20reality%20(right).%3Cp%3ENetflix%2C%20Jonathan%20McManus%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Full%20Moon%20Ball%20sees%20Penelope%20Featherington%20attempt%20to%20put%20Colin%20Bridgerton's%20husband-attracting%20lessons%20into%20practice.%20Elsewhere%2C%20Francesca%20Bridgerton%20makes%20a%20lasting%20impression%20on%20Queen%20Charlotte%20while%20playing%20the%20piano%20solo%2C%20thanks%20to%20Lady%20Danbury's%20social%20maneuvering.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFilming%20of%20the%20exterior%20shots%20of%20the%20ball's%20location%20took%20place%20at%20Osterly%20Park%20and%20House%2C%20a%20historic%20Georgian%20manor%20in%20Isleworth%2C%20not%20too%20far%20from%20central%20London.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuilt%20during%20Tudor%20times%20and%20renovated%20in%20the%2018th%20century%2C%20the%20once-privately-owned%20estate%20is%20now%20run%20by%20the%20UK's%20National%20Trust%20and%20is%20open%20to%20the%20public%20on%20select%20days%20and%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nationaltrust.org.uk%2Fvisit%2Flondon%2Fosterley-park-and-house%2Fthe-history-of-osterley-park%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENational%20Trust%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Osterly%20has%20also%20been