ds%20were%20heavily%20drunk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20are%20trying%20to%20build%20a%20watertight%20case%2C%20the%20top%20cop%20said%20on%20Tuesday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20visited%20us%20in%20May%20on%20the%203rd.%20It%20was%20my%20anniversary.%20So%20he%20was%20visiting%20us.%20He%20left%20on%20the%205th%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ms%20Awadhiya%20on%20her%20last%20meeting%20with%20her%20son%2C%20adding%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3Ewoh%20bahut%20achha%20bachha%20tha%2C%20sabko%20apna%20bana%20leta%20tha%3C%2Fem%3E%20(He%20was%20a%20good%20child.%20He%20was%20nice%20to%20everyone)%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EWoh%20bola%20mumma%20aapke%20liye%20main%20gift%20leke%20aaya%20hoon%20Dubai%20se.%20Chocolate%20aur%20khajoor.%20Toh%20main%20aaunga%20aap%20logon%20ko%20dene.%20Jaldi%20hi%20aane%20wala%20hoon.%20Lekin%20woh%20ho%20nahi%20paya%3C%2Fem%3E%20(He%20told%20me%20that%20he%20had%20got%20gifts%20for%20me%3A%20chocolates%20and%20dates.%20I%20will%20visit%20you%20soon.%20But%20that%20was%20not%20to%20be)%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20father%20of%20the%20teenager%20has%20been%20remanded%20in%20police%20custody%20for%20two%20days.%20The%20realtor%20was%20arrested%20on%20Tuesday%20from%20Chhatrapati%20Sambhajinagar%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20where%20he%20had%20allegedly%20gone%20to%20evade%20the%20cops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716405000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F64j18lb8_aneesh-pune-accident_650x400_22_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhe-killed-my-son-mother-of-man-killed-in-pune-porsche-accident-breaks-down-in-tears-5723414%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22She%20kept%20her%20composure%20for%20the%20first%20few%20questions.%20But%20gave%20in%20at%20the%20fourth%20minute%20and%20burst%20into%20tears.%20The%20woman%20was%20answering%20questions%20about%20her%20son%2C%20who%20was%20killed%20in%20the%20horrific%20Porsche%20crash%20in%20Pune%20in%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20Sunday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhe-killed-my-son-mother-of-man-killed-in-pune-porsche-accident-breaks-down-in-tears-5723414%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhe-killed-my-son-mother-of-man-killed-in-pune-porsche-accident-breaks-down-in-tears-5723414%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhe-killed-my-son-mother-of-man-killed-in-pune-porsche-accident-breaks-down-in-tears-5723414%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNon-Recovery%20Of%20Cash%20Can't%20Be...%26quot%3B%3A%20High%20Court%20In%20Manish%20Sisodia%20Hearing%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENon-recovery%20of%20cash%20cannot%20be%20a%20prima%20facie%20proof%20that%20no%20corruption%20has%20taken%20place%20as%20the%20offender's%20mind%20uses%20new%20technology%20to%20commit%20offences%20without%20leaving%20behind%20any%20trace%2C%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20has%20held%20while%20denying%20bail%20to%20AAP%20leader%20Manish%20Sisodia%20in%20the%20excise%20policy%20scam%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20said%20it%20cannot%20accept%20the%20argument%20put%20forth%20by%20Mr%20Sisodia%20about%20the%20non-recovery%20of%20cash%20from%20him%20in%20view%20of%20the%20statements%20of%20some%20hawala%20dealers%20and%20other%20witnesses%20recorded%20during%20the%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Swarana%20Kanta%20Sharma%20dismissed%20the%20bail%20pleas%20filed%20by%20the%20former%20Delhi%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20in%20the%20corruption%20and%20money%20laundering%20cases%20lodged%20by%20the%20CBI%20and%20ED%2C%20respectively%2C%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20alleged%20liquor%20scam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20two%20petitions%20were%20dismissed%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20detailed%20order%20was%20uploaded%20on%20the%20high%20court's%20website%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20court%20is%20of%20the%20view%20that%20the%20prosecution%20has%20made%20out%20a%20prima%20facie%20case%20of%20commission%20of%20money%20laundering%20under%20Section%203%20of%20PMLA%20against%20Manish%20Sisodia%2C%20at%20this%20stage.%20It%20is%20to%20be%20noted%20at%20the%20outset%20that%20the%20requirement%20of%20recovery%20of%20cash%20amount%20from%20a%20particular%20person%20may%20not%20necessarily%20be%20a%20mandatory%20requirement%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20case%20where%20the%20allegations%20are%20of%20being%20part%20of%20a%20conspiracy%20consisting%20of%20multiple%20accused%20persons%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20high%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20this%20court's%20opinion%2C%20non-recovery%20of%20any%20amount%20of%20money%20in%20cash%20cannot%20be%20a%20proof%20prima%20facie%20that%20no%20corruption%20has%20taken%20place%20since%20the%20offender%E2%80%98s%20mind%20uses%20the%20new%20technology%20to%20commit%20offences%20without%20leaving%20traces%20of%20commission%20of%20offences%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20observed%20that%20the%20case%20involves%20commission%20of%20%26quot%3Bserious%20offence%26quot%3B%20of%20corruption%20in%20public%20office%20and%20money%20laundering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20offences%20%26quot%3Bstrike%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20our%20economic%20and%20social%20systems%2C%20undermining%20the%20rule%20of%20law%20and%20eroding%20public%20trust%20in%20our%20institutions%26quot%3B%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMoreover%2C%20the%20form%20of%20corruption%20which%20has%20the%20tendency%20of%20stealing%20the%20legitimate%20resources%20of%20the%20poor%20ordinary%20people%20and%20giving%20it%20to%20the%20rich%20can%20be%20one%20of%20the%20worst%20forms%20of%20corruption%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20high%20court%20said%20in%20a%20106-page%20judgment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20small%20and%20medium-sized%20enterprises%2C%20which%20are%20managed%20by%20common%20people%20and%20are%20the%20backbone%20of%20economic%20growth%20and%20job%20creation%2C%20are%20particularly%20vulnerable%20to%20the%20detrimental%20impacts%20of%20corruption%20that%20is%20prima%20facie%20visible%20in%20the%20formulation%20of%20the%20new%20excise%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20the%20new%20excise%20policy%20has%20%E2%80%9Ceradicated%E2%80%9D%20the%20common%20and%20small-time%20businesses%20and%20gave%20the%20entire%20playing%20field%20in%20the%20liquor%20business%20to%20those%20who%20had%20%E2%80%9Cmoney%2C%20power%20and%20had%20created%20a%20cartel%E2%80%9D%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20financial%20gains%20to%20those%20formulating%20a%20policy%2C%20which%20adds%20to%20the%20seriousness%20of%20the%20offence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20courts%20of%20law%20may%20be%20considered%20as%20constant%20thorns%20in%20the%20way%20of%20free-flowing%20corruption%20and%2C%20even%20if%20that%20be%20so%20and%20are%20termed%20as%20thorns%2C%20it%20scores%20the%20victory%20for%20the%20masses%2C%E2%80%9D%20Justice%20Sharma%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20observed%20in%20its%20order%20that%20the%20matter%20involved%20grave%20misuse%20of%20power%20and%20breach%20of%20public%20trust%20by%20Mr%20Sisodia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20leader's%20conduct%20amounted%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bgreat%20betrayal%20of%20democratic%20principles%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20court%20said%2C%20adding%20he%20allegedly%20indulged%20in%20destruction%20of%20crucial%20evidence%2C%20including%20electronic%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20Mr%20Sisodia%20was%20a%20very%20influential%20person%20within%20the%20power%20corridors%20of%20the%20Delhi%20government%20as%20he%20had%20the%20responsibility%20of%2018%20portfolios%20in%20the%20city%20dispensation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20had%20challenged%20a%20trial%20court's%20April%2030%20order%20by%20which%20his%20bail%20pleas%20were%20rejected%20in%20the%20corruption%20and%20money%20laundering%20cases%20lodged%20by%20the%20CBI%20and%20ED%2C%20respectively%2C%20in%20connection%20with%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20the%20formulation%20and%20execution%20of%20the%20now-scrapped%20Delhi%20excise%20policy%20for%202021-22.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20seeking%20bail%20for%20Mr%20Sisodia%2C%20his%20counsel%20had%20submitted%20before%20the%20high%20court%20that%20the%20ED%20and%20CBI%20are%20still%20arresting%20people%20in%20the%20money%20laundering%20and%20corruption%20cases%2C%20and%20there%20is%20no%20question%20of%20early%20conclusion%20of%20the%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20the%20ED%20and%20CBI%20opposed%20Mr%20Sisodia's%20bail%20pleas%20on%20grounds%20that%20concerted%20efforts%20were%20made%20by%20the%20accused%20to%20delay%20the%20process%20of%20framing%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sisodia%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20CBI%20on%20February%2026%2C%202023%2C%20for%20his%20alleged%20role%20in%20the%20liquor%20%26quot%3Bscam%26quot%3B.%20The%20ED%20arrested%20him%20in%20the%20money%20laundering%20case%20stemming%20from%20the%20CBI%20FIR%20on%20March%209%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20resigned%20from%20the%20Delhi%20cabinet%20on%20February%2028%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20probe%20agencies%20have%20alleged%20that%20the%20beneficiaries%20diverted%20%26quot%3Billegal%26quot%3B%20gains%20to%20the%20accused%20officials%20and%20made%20false%20entries%20in%20their%20books%20of%20account%20to%20evade%20detection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20probe%20agencies%2C%20irregularities%20were%20committed%20while%20modifying%20the%20excise%20policy%20and%20undue%20favours%20were%20extended%20to%20the%20licence%20holders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20government%20implemented%20the%20policy%20on%20November%2017%2C%202021%2C%20but%20scrapped%20it%20at%20the%20end%20of%20September%202022%20amid%20allegations%20of%20corruption.%3C%2Fp%