ed%20because%20the%20BJP%20is%20committed%20to%20the%20%26quot%3BNation%20First%26quot%3B%20model.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20Opposition%20bloc%20--%20their%20only%20agenda%20is%20'Family%20First'.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20this%20very%20Delhi%2C%20my%20Sikh%20brothers%20and%20sisters%20were%20killed%20by%20placing%20burning%20tyres%20around%20their%20neck.%20Today%2C%20every%20party%20under%20the%20Congress%20umbrella%20stands%20guilty%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20citing%20the%20anti-Sikh%20riots%20of%201984%20after%20the%20assassination%20of%20then%20Prime%20Minister%20Indira%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAAP%20and%20Congress%20are%20contesting%20in%20Delhi%20under%20a%20seat-sharing%20deal%20that%20allotted%20four%20seats%20to%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20party%20and%20three%20to%20the%20Congress.%20The%20two%20parties%2C%20though%2C%20are%20contesting%20against%20each%20other%20in%20Punjab%2C%20with%20the%20respective%20state%20units%20unable%20to%20bury%20the%20hatchet.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20going%20solo%20in%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20contesting%20all%20seven%20seats.%20In%202019%2C%20the%20party%20had%20swept%20the%20capital%20and%20is%20now%20hoping%20for%20a%20repeat%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAAP%2C%20determined%20to%20put%20up%20a%20strong%20fight%2C%20found%20itself%20stymied%20after%20the%20arrest%20of%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20Delhi%20liquor%20policy%20case.%20But%20since%20his%20release%20on%20interim%20bail%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20the%20party%20has%20got%20a%20fresh%20boost.%20Two%20of%20its%20other%20key%20leaders%2C%20Manish%20Sisodia%20and%20Satyendar%20Jain%2C%20though%2C%20are%20still%20in%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20AAP%20and%20Congress%20had%20contested%20separately%2C%20playing%20into%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20BJP.%20This%20time%2C%20the%20two%20parties%20are%20hoping%20that%20their%20alliance%20would%20help