2%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc3gg87kwl0eo.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Making%20Form%2017C%20Data%20Public%20Will%20Cause%20Confusion%20Among%20Voters%3A%20Poll%20Body%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20on%20Wednesday%20filed%20an%20affidavit%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20saying%20disclosure%20of%20voter%20turnout%20data%20based%20on%20Form%2017C%20(records%20of%20votes%20polled%20in%20each%20polling%20station)%20will%20cause%20confusion%20among%20voters%20as%20it%20will%20also%20include%20postal%20ballot%20counts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ECI%20in%20an%20affidavit%20filed%20before%20the%20top%20court%20contended%20that%20there%20is%20no%20legal%20right%20that%20can%20be%20claimed%20towards%20publishing%20final%20authenticated%20data%20of%20voter%20turnout%20in%20all%20polling%20stations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20uploading%20of%20Form%2017C%20on%20the%20website%20can%20lead%20to%20mischief%20and%20that%20there%20are%20possibilities%20of%20images%20being%20morphed%2C%20which%20can%20create%20%26quot%3Bwidespread%20discomfort%20and%20mistrust%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20any%20electoral%20contest%2C%20the%20margin%20of%20victory%20may%20be%20very%20close.%20In%20such%20cases%2C%20disclosure%20of%20Form%2017C%20in%20public%20domain%20may%20cause%20confusion%20in%20the%20minds%20of%20the%20voters%20with%20regard%20to%20the%20total%20votes%20polled%20as%20the%20latter%20figure%20would%20include%20the%20number%20of%20votes%20polled%20as%20per%20Form%2017C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20votes%20received%20through%20postal%20ballots.%20However%2C%20such%20difference%20may%20not%20be%20easily%20understood%20by%20the%20voters%20and%20may%20be%20used%20by%20persons%20with%20motivated%20interests%20to%20cast%20aspersion%20on%20the%20whole%20electoral%20process...%20cause%20chaos%20in%20the%20election%20machinery%20which%20is%20already%20in%20motion%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20affidavit%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20further%20stated%20that%20as%20per%20rules%2C%20Form%2017C%20needs%20to%20be%20given%20only%20to%20the%20polling%20agent%20and%20rules%20do%20not%20permit%20the%20giving%20of%20Form%2017C%20to%20any%20other%20entity.%20General%20disclosure%20of%20Form%2017C%20to%20public%20is%20not%20contemplated%20by%20Rules%2C%20ECI%20told%20the%20top%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20poll%20panel%20filed%20the%20affidavit%20on%20an%20application%20by%20NGO%20Association%20for%20Democratic%20Reforms%20(ADR)%20seeking%20disclosure%20of%20final%20authenticated%20data%20of%20voter%20turnout%20in%20all%20polling%20stations%20including%20the%20number%20of%20votes%20polled%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Elections%202024%20within%2048%20hours%20of%20the%20polling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ECI%20sought%20dismissal%20of%20application%20filed%20by%20ADR%20saying%20that%20certain%20%26quot%3Bvested%20interests%26quot%3B%20keep%20on%20throwing%20false%20allegations%20at%20it%20to%20discredit%20its%20working.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20asked%20ECI%20to%20file%20its%20response%20on%20the%20application%20seeking%20direction%20to%20immediately%20upload%20account%20of%20votes%20recorded%20of%20all%20polling%20stations%20after%20the%20close%20of%20polling%20of%20each%20phase%20in%20the%20ongoing%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NGO%20ADR%20alleged%20inordinate%20delay%20in%20the%20publication%20of%20voter%20turnout%20data%20of%20the%20first%20two%20phases%20of%20polling%20in%20the%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20application%2C%20besides%20delay%20in%20publishing%20the%20voter-turnout%20details%2C%20said%20there%20was%20a%20sharp%20spike%20in%20figures%20from%20the%20initial%20voter%20turnout%20percentages%20released%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20sought%20a%20direction%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20to%20provide%20tabulated%20polling%20station-wise%20data%20in%20absolute%20figures%20of%20the%20number%20of%20votes%20polled%20as%20recorded%2C%20in%20Form%2017C%20Part-%20I%2C%20after%20each%20phase%20of%20polling%20in%20the%20ongoing%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20and%20also%20a%20tabulation%20of%20constituency-wise%20figures%20of%20voter%20turnout%20in%20absolute%20numbers%20in%20the%20on-going%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20further%20asked%20for%20uploading%20on%20the%20ECI%20website%20the%20scanned%20legible%20copies%20of%20Form%2017C%20Part-%20II%20which%20contained%20the%20candidate-wise%20result%20of%20counting%20after%20the%20compilation%20of%20results%20of%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20application%20said%20the%20voter%20turnout%20data%20for%20the%20first%20two%20phases%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20were%20published%20by%20the%20ECI%20on%20April%2030%2C%20after%2011%20days%20of%20the%20first%20phase%20of%20polling%20held%20on%20April%2019%20and%20four%20days%20after%20the%20second%20phase%20of%20polling%20held%20on%20April%2026.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20that%20the%20data%20published%20by%20the%20ECI%20in%20its%20April%2030%20press%20release%20showed%20a%20sharp%20increase%20(by%20about%205-6%20per%20cent)%20from%20the%20initial%20percentages%20announced%20by%20it%20on%20the%20polling%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NGO%20pointed%20out%20the%20data%20published%20in%20the%20press%20release%20by%20the%20ECI%20on%20April%2030%2C%202024%20(Phase%20I%20voter%20turnout-%2066.14%20per%20cent%20and%20Phase%20II%20voter%20turnout%20-%2066.71%20per%20cent)%20when%20compared%20with%20the%20initial%20data%20of%20April%2019%2C%202024%20and%20April%2026%2C%202024%20respectively%20showed%20an%20increase%20of%20nearly%206%20per%20cent%20in%20the%20Phase%20I%20data%20and%20increase%20of%20approximately%205.75%20per%20cent%20in%20the%20Phase%20II%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20b