isfying%20for%20Manish.%20%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20doctors%20cannot%20get%20away%20with%20citing%20unknown%20reasons%20and%20have%20to%20mention%20satisfactory%20reasons%20in%20their%20postmortem%20reports%20so%20that%20farmers%20settle%20insurance%20claims.%20Meanwhile%2C%20we%20have%20been%20able%20to%20boost%20the%20incomes%20of%20farmer%20families%20by%2040%20percent.%20They%20are%20able%20to%20wed%20their%20daughters%20by%20selling%20good%20breed%20bovines.%20To%20be%20able%20to%20work%20for%20millions%20of%20voiceless%20animals%20and%20farmer%20families%20gives%20me%20immense%20fulfilment%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Manish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fatariz1.icar.gov.in%2Fpdf%2FLumpy%2520Skin%2520Disease.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELumpy%20Skin%20Disease%20Emerging%20Threat%20to%20Livestock%20Industry%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20Published%20by%20ICAR%20-Agricultural%20Technology%20Application%20Research%20Institute%20(ATARI)%20in%20March%202023.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Manish%20Prahlad.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716385342000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FManish-Prahlad-1716381129.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D350767%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20losing%20his%20buffaloes%20mysteriously%2C%20Jaipur-based%20Manish%20Prahlad%20launched%20Verdant%20Impact%20%E2%80%94%20a%20startup%20offering%20telemedicine%2C%20animal%20ICU%2C%20and%20other%20veterinary%20services%20to%20farmers%20to%20improve%20livestock%20healthcare%20in%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F350767%2Fcattle