the%20engineer%20slowly%20grew%20to%20realise%20that%20she%20had%20a%20green%20thumb.%20From%20indoor%20plants%2C%20she%20branched%20to%20vegetables%20and%20fruits%20on%20the%201%2C000%20square%20feet%20terrace%20of%20her%20rented%20apartment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20it%20has%20grown%20into%20a%20green%20haven%20with%20over%20300%20plants%2C%2070%20of%20which%20are%20fruit%20trees.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProviding%20Sushma%20with%20a%20much-needed%20outlet%20for%20her%20worries%2C%20she%20spends%20three%20hours%20a%20day%20tending%20to%20her%20darling%20plants%2C%20all%20on%20her%20own.%20Her%20passion%20also%20led%20to%20an%20Instagram%20account%20%40glitters.of.nature%20which%20has%20over%204%20lakh%20followers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20adds%20to%20this%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F303953%2Fshashi-manchanda-homemaker-grows-organic-vegetables-flowers-on-terrace-garden-gurugram%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eterrace%20gardener%E2%80%99s%20feat%20%3C%2Fa%3Eis%20the%20fact%20that%20all%20her%20plants%2C%20including%20her%20fruit%20trees%20are%20grown%20on%2010-16%20inch%20pots!%20She%20shares%20her%20story%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilding%20a%20garden%2C%20and%20a%20home%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHailing%20from%20Visakhapatnam%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20Sushma%20moved%20to%20Bengaluru%20post%20marriage.%20When%20her%20son%20was%20born%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20the%20new%20parents%20started%20noticing%20some%20developmental%20delays%2C%20especially%20with%20regards%20to%20speech.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201920px)%20100vw%2C%201920px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FSushma1-1715673962.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Su