f%20the%20valley%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Himani.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDay%204%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20trekked%20from%20Ghangaria%20to%20Hemkund%20Sahib%2C%20which%20is%20a%20steep%20climb%20but%20worth%20the%20effort.%20At%20the%20top%2C%20we%20enjoyed%20the%20Gurudwara%20and%20the%20serene%20lake.%20Hemkund%20Sahib%20is%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20highest%20Gurudwara%20at%204%2C329%20m.%20We%20had%20a%20delicious%20meal%20at%20the%20Langar%20and%20then%20trekked%20back%20down%20to%20Ghangaria%20to%20stay%20the%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDay%205%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe%20started%20our%20journey%20back%20from%20Ghangaria%20to%20Govindghat%2C%20which%20took%20about%205%20hours.%20After%20lunch%20in%20Govindghat%2C%20we%20drove%20back%20to%20Joshimath%20and%20stayed%20overnight%20at%20the%20local%20guest%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMake%20sure%20you%20carry%20all%20your%20medicines%2C%20a%20raincoat%20in%20the%20monsoons%20and%20ample%20amount%20of%20drinking%20water%20before%20you%20go%20on%20the%20trek.%20Once%20you%20are%20inside%20the%20valley%2C%20there%20are%20no%20shops%20or%20caretakers%20to%20help%20you%20out%2C%20the%20couple%20advises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhere%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20magical%20valley%3F%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKeeping%20in%20mind%20your%20flights%2Ftrain%20timings%2C%20you%20might%20consider%20staying%20to%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F345629%2Fmuthunandhini-palace-kanyakumari-ecofriendly-homestay-chettinad-architecture-tamil-nadu-travel-destination%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20book%20a%20stay%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Rishikesh.%20Here%20are%20some%20homestays%20and%20hostels%20that%20you%20can%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.homestaysofindia.com%2F%3Fs%3Drishikesh%2B%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebook%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E