0100vw%2C%20960px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Ftrue1-1715860659.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22True%20Elements%20has%20a%20factory%20in%20Pune%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Ftrue1-1715860659.jpeg%20960w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Ftrue1-1715860659-300x291.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Ftrue1-1715860659-500x484.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Ftrue1-1715860659-768x744.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Ftrue1-1715860659-150x145.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-350256%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22930%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETrue%20Elements%20has%20a%20factory%20in%20Pune%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20to%20choose%20a%20partner%20who%20would%20align%20with%20our%20vision%20and%20understand%20health.%20We%20both%20were%20also%20clear%2C%20right%20from%20the%20beginning%2C%20that%20we%20wanted%20to%20create%20something%20that%20would%20outlive%20us.%20This%20acquisition%20would%20help%20our%20objective%20come%20true%20and%20make%20%E2%80%98True%20Elements%E2%80%99%20a%20household%20brand%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20COO.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20today%E2%80%99s%20competitive%20healthy%20food%20space%2C%20the%20founders%20believe%20that%20their%20differentiation%20lies%20in%20the%20transparency%20with%20regard%20to%20their%20products.%20All%20their%20products%20have%20complete%20ingredients%20listed%20behind%20them%20and%20an%20option%20to%20trace%20the%20ingredient%E2%80%99s%20journey%20from%20farm%20to%20fork%20on%20their%20website%20using%20the%20product%20name%20and%20batch%20number.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20founders%20share%20that%20their%20startup%20rests