Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20overthink%2C%20just%20start%20up.%20There%20will%20never%20be%20a%20perfect%20time.%20Dive%20in%20with%20a%20childlike%20mindset%2C%20and%20just%20like%20children%20do%20when%20they%20fall%20down%2C%20stand%20up%20and%20try%20again.%20It%E2%80%99s%20okay%20to%20fall%20down%20and%20fail.%20Shun%20the%20need%20for%20validation%20and%20fear%20of%20judgement%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Puru.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20all%20the%20youngsters%20who%20believe%20that%20you%20can%20succeed%20in%20a%20year%2C%20Sreejith%20has%20some%20words%20of%20wisdom.%20%E2%80%9CNo%20one%20arrives%20in%20a%20year%2C%20it%20takes%20at%20least%20six%20years.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20give%20up%20before%20these%20six%20to%20seven%20years%20and%20don%E2%80%99t%20be%20afraid%20of%20going%20down%20to%20zero%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Sreejith.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%2C%20Images%20Courtesy%20True%20Elements%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715929549000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FCover-image-15-1715860333.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D350165%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sreejith%20Moolayil%20and%20Puru%20Gupta%20overcame%20challenges%20to%20build%20their%20healthy%20food%20brand%2C%20True%20Elements.%20Despite%20early%20failures%20and%20financial%20struggles%2C%20their%20commitment%20to%20preventative%20healthcare%20and%20transparency%20led%20to%20a%20multi-crore%20business.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F350165%2Fpuru-gupta-sreejith-moolayil-true-elements-pune-marico-healthy-snacks-rolled-oats-muesli-chia-seeds%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20an%2087-YO%20Trained%201%20Lakh%20Indians%20On%20How%20to%20Save%20Lives%20After%20Road%20Accidents%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EReflecting%20on%20when%20she%20received%20the%20Padma%20Shri%20award%20for%20her%20contributions%20to%20road%20safety%20in%20India%2C%20Dr%20Maya%20Tandon%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20the%20greatest%20moment%20of%20my%20life.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2087-year-old%20retired%20anesthesiologist%20has%20devoted%20her%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F142778%2Fassam-dgp-cop-maths-teacher-govt-school%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20post-retirement%20years%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20making%20Indian%20roads%20safer.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20many%20are%20familiar%20with%20road%20safety%20protocols%20and%20first%20aid%2C%20few%20know%20how%20to%20perform%20them%20effectively%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Maya%20trains%20people%20in%20road%20safety%20through%20her%20organisation%20%E2%80%98Sahayta%20Trust%E2%80%99.%20Working%20relentlessly%20for%20the%20past%20three%20decades%2C%20she%20says%20she%20has%20trained%201%2C33%2C000%20people%20in%20road%20safety%2C%20CRP%20(cardiopulmonary%20resuscitation)%2C%20sequential%20handling%2C%20and%20protocol%20dealings%20with%20accidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20zeal%20for%20life%20and%20a%20passion%20for%20working%20for%20society%20%E2%80%94%20stronger%20than%20ever%20%E2%80%94%20Dr%20Maya%20reflects%20on%20her%20journey%20and%20shares%20what%20led%20her%20to%20this%20path.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhen%20saving%20lives%20became%20her%20mission%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20raised%20in%20Ajmer%2C%20Dr%20Maya%20was%20a%20starry-eyed%20child%20who%20dreamt%20of%20doing%20something%20great.%20%E2%80%9CGiven%20the%20times%20that%20I%20was%20born%20in%2C%20my%20family%20was%20very%20supportive%20and%20liberal.%20I%20scored%20good%20marks%20on%20the%20school%20board%20exams%20and%20got%20admitted%20to%20medical%20school%20in%20Ajmer%20and%20Delhi%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20grew%20up%20in%20luxury%2C%20which%20allowed%20her%20the%20freedom%20to%20choose%20her%20own%20path%20in%20life.%20So%20she%20decided%20to%20pursue%20a%20career%20in%20medical%20science.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20did%20my%20internship%20in%20Ajmer%2C%20where%20I%20met%20my%20husband.%20We%20decided%20to%20get%20married%20and%20moved%20to%20Jaipur%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201968%2C%20Dr%20Maya%20gave%20birth%20to%20her%20son.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20that%2C%20I%20chose%20to%20pursue%20a%20diploma%20in%20anesthesiology%20because%20it%20was%20a%20career%20that%20I%20could%20manage%20while%20raising%20a%20family.%20By%20the%20time%20I%20completed%20my%20diploma%2C%20I%20had%20also%20given%20birth%20to%20another%20child%2C%20my%20daughter%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201972%2C%20she%20also%20did%20an%20MS%20in%20anaesthesia.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20also%20giving%20lectures%20on%20anaesthesia%20at%20a%20medical%20college%20in%20Jaipur%20where%20I%20came%20across%20an%20opportunity.%20It%20was%20a%20fellowship%20in%20London%20for%20paediatric%20anaesthesia.%20With%20my%20family%E2%80%99s%20support%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20attend%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-6-1715867697.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-6-1715867697.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-6-1715867697-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-6-1715867697-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-6-1715867697-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-6-1715867697-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-350314%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDr%20Maya%20Tandon%2C%20a%20Padma%20Shri%20Awardee.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20completing%20her%20fellowship%2C%20she%20returned%20to%20India%20and%20began%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F251637%2Frajasthan-startup-newndra-innovation-ganesh-ram-jangir-jaipur-belt-back-pain-farmer-help-make-in-india-ros174%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworking%20in%20Jaipur.%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fa%3EThe%20role%20of%20an%20anesthesiologist%20is%20often%20seen%20as%20a%20behind-the-curtain%20job.%20However%2C%20for%20me%20and%20in%20medical%20sciences%2C%20the%20patient%E2%80%99s%20life%20depends%20on%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20emphasises%2C%20highlighting%20her%20deep%20interest%20in%20lifesaving%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201975%2C%20she%20earned%20the%20honour%20of%20becoming%20superintendent%20and%20spent%20the%20rest%20of%20her%20career%20managing%20the%20hospital%20while%20serving%20as%20the%20head%20of%20anaesthesia%20at%20Sawai%20Man%20Singh%20Hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20around%20the%20time%20of%20my%20retirement%20in%201985%20when%20the%20Rajasthan%20Police%20Academy%20in%20Jaipur%20contacted%20me%20and%20requested%20I%20give%20a%20three-day%20course%20on%20road%20safety%20and%20lifesaving.%20I%20readily%20agreed%20to%20the%20request%2C%20unaware%20that%20it%20would%20shape%20the%20course%20of%20my%20post-retirement%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Maya%20reminisces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20course%20was%20very%20successful%20and%20all%20the%20senior%20officers%20posted%20on%20highways%20in%20and%20around%20Jaipur%20were%20sent%20to%20her%20for%20yet%20another%20course.%20%E2%80%9CA%20photographer%20had%20come%20to%20take%20some%20pictures%20of%20the%20event.%20It%20was%20a%20few%20months%20later%20that%20he%20rang%20me%20up%20and%20told%20me%20that%20I%20had%20saved%20his%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20photographer%20had%20been%20in%20an%20accident%20and%20could%20feel%20bleeding%20in%20his%20inner%20thighs%20and%20back.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20people%20around%20him%20were%20not%20sure%20how%20to%20help%20him%20and%20were%20taking%20pictures%20of%20him.%20He%20explained%20someone%20to%20lift%20him%20and%20put%20him%20in%20a%20certain%20position%20that%20slowed%20the%20bleeding%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20narrates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20timely%20move%20reduced%20the%20blood%20loss%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F317185%2Fbollywood-celebrity-photographer-munna-thaakur-recalls-struggle-story%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaved%20the%20photographer%E2%80%99s%20life.%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%9CHis%20words%20and%20appreciation%20made%20me%20realise%20the%20importance%20of%20offering%20such%20courses.%20It%20also%20revealed%20the%20sad%20reality%20of%20the%20state%20of%20road%20safety%20in%20India.%20Not%20one%20of%20the%20persons%20in%20the%20crowd%20knew%20lifesaving%20steps%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20an%20intention%20to%20change%20the%20scenario%20of%20road%20safety%20in%20India%2C%20Dr%20Maya%20started%20the%20Sahayta%20Trust.%20Since%20then%2C%20she%20has%20given%20free%20courses%2C%20seminars%2C%20and%20lectures%20to%20over%201%2C33%2C000%20individuals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20these%20courses%20are%20conducted%20free%20of%20charge.%20The%20aim%20is%20to%20raise%20awareness%20about%20CPR%20(cardiopulmonary%20resuscitation)%2C%20proper%20handling%20tech